
To apply for leave from February 27 to March 15, you can follow this sample format for a formal leave application:

Subject: Leave Application from February 27 to March 15

Dear [Manager's Name],

I hope this message finds you well. I am writing to request a leave of absence from February 27, 2024, to March 15, 2024 (inclusive) due to [mention reason, if necessary: personal reasons, vacation, medical reasons, etc.].

I have ensured that all pending tasks are completed, and I will hand over any ongoing work to [colleague/team] before my departure. Please let me know if any additional preparations are needed from my end.

Thank you for your understanding and support.

Sincerely,
[Your Name]
[Your Position]
